{"tid":2427294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方在沙田馬場拘捕3名男子 涉非法收受賭注","createTime":"2021-02-28T16:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T16:45:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4ac07e87a44e673d93b6f00bb4c9c2eb837bfe","tid":2427294,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"警方昨日在沙田馬場拘捕3名男子，介乎43至44歲，涉嫌非法收受賭注。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查顯示，有人在沙田馬場收受外圍賭注，觀察馬匹開跑後的狀態，然後以手提電腦登入非法賭博網站，於賽事期間投注。<br />\n<br />\n警方檢獲6部手提電話、3部手提電腦、約2萬6千元現金以及約960萬元的懷疑外圍投注紀錄，不排除會有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578008-20210301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578008-20210301.htm&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3SZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=fc3c0202\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578008-20210301.htm&h=b2d94e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578008-20210301.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bdf1bf0699ddb787a9b2dc783cb1fd437a2ab58c","tid":2427294,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:45:41.000Z","msg":"唔知外圍狗係咪裝左安心出殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}